Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.68,0:01:13.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,arekore fukaku kangaeru no wa Mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:20.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,Hora unmei no hito wa soko ni iru
